name: Dr Seauss Cat in a Hat Bunting
description:
Price is for a personalised bunting with a name of 5 letters. Binding for this bunting will be a total length of 2 meters.
                        6 flags = 2.2m
                        7 flags = 2.4m
                        8 flags = 2.6m
                        9 flags = 2.8m


Additional Letters or blank flags options can be purchased below. Simply select the correct amount of letters required for the "NAME" on the bunting and options of blank flags either side of your name ie. 1 either side of name (2 blank flags) or 2 either side of name (4 blank flags)

The bunting features fabric from the Dr Seauss Range

Each letter is hand embroided with blanket stitch. Please state "NAME" when completing transaction.


IF YOU CAN NOT FIND YOUR PREFERRED OPTION BELOW PLEASE CONTACT ME AND A CUSTOM ORDER CAN BE CREATED.
